WEBVTT

00:01.980 --> 00:04.540
<i>My name is Earl.</i>

00:04.650 --> 00:07.710
<i>[Earl Narrating]</i>
<i>Ernie's Crab Shack was named after three things:</i>

00:07.820 --> 00:09.720
<i>The food they're most famous for...</i>

00:09.820 --> 00:13.250
<i>the type ofbuilding it was</i>
<i>and the owner- Ernie Belcher.</i>

00:13.350 --> 00:16.080
<i>And after 54 years ofbeing in business...</i>

00:16.190 --> 00:18.320
<i>the crabs and the Shack are still around...</i>

00:18.430 --> 00:20.520
<i>but old Ernie's been missin'for years.</i>

00:20.630 --> 00:23.890
<i>And until today, we never thought</i>
<i>we'd find out what happened to him.</i>

00:24.000 --> 00:26.660
It's comin' on! Oh, my God! It's comin' on!

00:26.770 --> 00:30.570
It's comin' on, it's comin' on,
it's comin' on, it's comin' on.

00:30.670 --> 00:32.830
Our <i>Inside Probe</i> is finally comin' on.

00:32.940 --> 00:35.140
- Man, I can't believe they're finally gonna air that.
- <i>[TVOn]</i>

00:35.240 --> 00:38.340
It's been, like, eight years.
I wonder what took 'em so long.

00:38.450 --> 00:41.510
Actually, that's my fault. Now that
I'm no longer in Witness Protection...

00:41.620 --> 00:43.520
I was able to finally sign
the release papers.

00:43.620 --> 00:45.310
Next week, my <i>Wheel of Fortune</i> will air.

00:45.420 --> 00:47.980
All day long
with that Witness Protection mess.

00:48.090 --> 00:49.490
How long you gonna milk that thing?

00:49.590 --> 00:51.580
We all got stories we're proud of.

00:51.690 --> 00:53.590
I went to the prom as a sixth grader.

00:53.690 --> 00:56.360
Now shut up. It's startin'.

00:56.460 --> 01:00.460
