01:08.580 --> 01:11.600
Eight years ago, we visited
the small town of Camden...

01:11.710 --> 01:15.080
<i>where a search for the missing owner</i>
<i>of a seafood restaurant...</i>

01:15.180 --> 01:17.810
<i>uncovers some</i> fishy <i>details...</i>

01:17.920 --> 01:20.320
<i>and an</i> ocean <i>of possibilities.</i>

